children.description: Question: Could you please provide the tracking number for your package? This information is necessary to retrieve carrier details.
I need to detect the carrier for this tracking number first. Once I have that information, I can provide you with the carrier details. I will proceed with the detection now.

I successfully detected the carriers for your tracking number. The package can be tracked by either "Royal Mail" or "UBI Logistics". 

Next, I will get detailed tracking information for the package using one of these carriers, starting with Royal Mail.
It seems that there is no tracking information available for your package using "Royal Mail." Next, I'll try to get the tracking details using the other carrier, "UBI Logistics".

Unfortunately, I'm unable to retrieve any tracking information for your package from both Royal Mail and UBI Logistics. This might happen if the tracking number is incorrect, or the package has not been updated in their system yet.

Now I will wrap up this task.

{"final_answer":"I couldn't retrieve any tracking details for the package with tracking number 'NY323068998GB' from both detected carriers: Royal Mail and UBI Logistics. Please check the tracking number or try again later.","return_type":"give_answer"}
